<%@ page contentType="text/html;charset=UTF-8" language="java" %><%@ taglib prefix="c" uri="http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/core" %><!doctype html><html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><title>File Import</title></head><body><h1>File Dropbox Import Lab</h1><nav><a href="${pageContext.request.contextPath}/ops">Ops</a> | <a href="${pageContext.request.contextPath}/settlements">Settlements</a></nav><p>파일은 D:/workspace/kjspringweb-legacy/dropbox 아래에 있다고 가정한다.</p><form method="post" action="${pageContext.request.contextPath}/file-import/register"><input name="fileName" placeholder="fileName.csv"><input name="expectedRows" placeholder="expectedRows"><button>Register</button></form><table border="1"><tr><th>ID</th><th>File</th><th>Expected</th><th>Status</th><th>Process</th></tr><c:forEach var="m" items="${manifests}"><tr><td>${m.id}</td><td>${m.fileName}</td><td>${m.expectedRows}</td><td>${m.status}</td><td><form method="post" action="${pageContext.request.contextPath}/file-import/${m.id}/process"><button>Process</button></form></td></tr></c:forEach></table></body></html>